scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: Pieces included: 1 score, 1 CD, 1 submission letter, 1 biographical and program note. Notes: Note on envelope: HD2.1 .07, HD2.2 .07, HD2.3 .04. Composer's signature inside front cover of score. Blue on black II has variable instrumentation. .
